# ============================================
# Life-OS .gitignore
# Public system (GitHub) vs Private data (local only)
# Cloud scheduled tasks need: CLAUDE.md, agents, skills, METRICS.md
# ============================================

# --- PRIVATE: Personal accountability data ---
Days/*.md
!Days/README.md
wins.md
waiting.md
decisions.md
inbox.md

# --- PRIVATE: Financial data ---
Finance/
ACCOUNTING.md
STATUS.md
WEEKLY-LOG.md

# --- PRIVATE: People with deal values ---
People/

# --- PRIVATE: Psychology frameworks ---
OCTOPUS.md
THE-DESCENT.md
THE-OCEAN.md
NOAH-REESE-VISION.md
GCH.md
BOTTLENECK.md

# --- PRIVATE: Deal tactics ---
Learning/DEALCRAFT.md
Learning/NEGOTIATION-SKILLS.md
