# --- PRIVATE: Briefings (contain personal data) ---
briefings/daily-ops/
briefings/im-business/
briefings/alchemy/
briefings/handoff-latest.md
briefings/urgent.md
briefings/completed.md
briefings/activity.log
# Keep singularity HTML for demos
briefings/singularity/*.md

