# --- SYSTEM: Build artifacts ---
node_modules/
.claude/telegram/node_modules/
.vercel/
*.log
bash.exe.stackdump
.mcp.json
transfer/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.playwright-mcp/
desktop.ini
LOS.pdf
transfer.zip
bash_aliases.txt
Untitled.canvas
"Days/Untitled 1.base"
Days/Untitled.base

# --- PUBLIC: The OS itself (what cloud tasks need) ---
# CLAUDE.md - YES push (system instructions)
# METRICS.md - YES push (scoring framework, no personal values)
# .claude/agents/ - YES push (all agent definitions)
# .claude/skills/ - YES push (all skill definitions)
# .claude/hooks/ - YES push (hook scripts)
# .claude/autonomous/*.ps1 - YES push (script templates)
# Tools/ - YES push (minus credentials)
# Templates/ - YES push
# Projects/ICS/*.md - YES push (research, no deal values)
# briefings/singularity/*.html - YES push (demo-worthy)
# briefings/BRIEFING-INDEX.md - YES push
# briefings/README.md - YES push
